  "article_text": "Welcome to the Star Atlas weekly recap from the Intergalactic Herald. Below is what happened with Star Atlas this past week.\nFloyd Line Aerospace One Review- Cinematic STAR ATLAS Showroom\nGladiator posted a video reviewing the Star Atlas Floyd Line ship.\nStar Atlas – Q1 2023 Development Sneak Peeks [WIP]\nStar Atlas posted a video showing some work-in-progress images of Star Atlas.\nSTAR ATLAS #170 Racing Track, Economic Report & Dev Update Video\nMetaVerse Explorer posted a video talking about the latest Star Atlas updates.\nStar Atlas Economic Report 2023 Q1\nStar Atlas published its latest Star Atlas Economic Report.\nMetaverse Nomads #88\nMetaverse Nomads posted a video of their weekly Star Atlas live stream.\nSTAR ATLAS Showroom with Gladiator 1080p\nGladiator posted a video reviewing the Star Atlas Showroom.\nStar Atlas SAGE Announcement and Quarterly Econ Update ft. Courtney\nHologram News Network posted a video with the latest Star Atlas updates.\nWEEKLY STAR ATLAS NEWSLETTER #73\nAephia published their weekly Star Atlas newsletter.\nSTAR ATLAS #171 Opal BitBoat Vs Rainbow Arc-Aid, Who wins!?\nMetaVerse Explorer posted a video comparing two Star Atlas ships.\nStar Atlas – “Shaping the Zeitgeist: Setting the Standard for Web3 Economies”\nThe Hologram News Network posted a video of an interview about the Star Atlas economy.",
